20.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  Go forth of Babylon, thou  that fleest from the Chaldeans: utter aloud a voice of joy, and let this be made known, proclaim it to the end of the earth; say ye, The Lord  hath delivered his servant Jacob. }21.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  And if they shall thirst, he shall lead them
