e Gentiles; after a long time it shall come to pass, saith the Lord: from my mother's  womb he has called my name: }2.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  and he has made my mouth as a sharp sword, and he has hid me under the shadow of his hand; he has  made me as a choice shaft, and he has h
id me in his quiver; }3.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  and said to me, Thou art my servant, O Israel, and in thee I will be glorified.  }4.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  Then I said, I have labored in vain, I have given my strength for vanity and for nothing: therefore is my judgment with the Lord, and my  labor befo
re my God.   }}
