not toward me as before but  the God of my father was with me. }6.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  And ye too know that with all my might I have served your father. }7.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  But your father deceived me,  and changed my wages for the ten lambs, yet God gave him lion power to hurt me. }8.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  If lie s
hould say thus, The speckled shall be thy  reward, then the cattle would bear speckled; and if he should say The white shall be thy reward, then would all the cattle bear white. }9.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  So  God has taken away all the cattle of your father, and given them to me.
 }10.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  And it came to pass when the cattle conceived and were with  young that beheld with mine eyes in sleep, and behold the he-goats and the rams leaping on the sheep and the she-goats, speckled and  variegated and spotted with ash-coloured spots. }11.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033   And
 the angel of God said to me in a dream, Jacob; and I said, What is it? }12.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033   And  he said, Look up with thine eyes, and behold the he-goats and the rams leaping on the sheep and the she-goats, speckled and variegated  and spotted with ash-coloured spots;  
I have seen all things that Laban does to thee. }13.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  I am God that appeared to thee in the place of  God, where thou anointedst a pillar to me, and vowedst to me there a vow; now then arise and depart out of this land, depart into the land  of thy nativity,
 and I will be with thee. }14.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033   And Rachel and Lea answered and said to him Have we yet a part of inheritance in the house  of our father? }15.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033   Are we not considered strangers by him? for he has sold us, and quite devoured our money. }16.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  All the wealth and 
the  glory which God has taken from our father, it shall be ours and our children's; now then do whatsoever God has said to thee.   }}
