shall be judged, and all flesh with his sword: many shall be slain by the Lord. }17.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  They that sanctify  themselves and purify themselves in the gardens, and eat swine's flesh in the porches, and the abominations, and the mouse, shall be  consumed together,
 saith the Lord. }18.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  And I [know] their works and their imagination. I am going to gather all nations and tongues; and  they shall come, and see my glory. }19.{\*\cs21\cf0\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\f2\fs32\lang1033\loch\f2\fs32\lang1033  And I will leave a sign upon them, and I will send forth them that have escaped of them to the  n
